        "text": "<h2>Troubleshooting Hardware Activity</h2>\nUse the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/12cuoprpjClVYBoBw0B7FdqrGaKGaOlexuj8VK3-vZds/edit?usp=sharing\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Activity Guide</a>  to explore the panels and analyze each step of the SNOT strategy. <br><br>In the next level, you'll refine your analysis using an AI chatbot. You don’t need to complete the activity—just get a sense of what your students will be doing.",
